Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.18,0:00:05.83,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.83,0:00:09.15,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It doesn't seem that my new role as a princess equates to all that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.15,0:00:12.62,Tirek,,0,0,0,,I am Lord Tirek.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.62,0:00:17.33,Tirek,,0,0,0,,And I will take what should have been mine long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.33,0:00:20.54,Luna,,0,0,0,,With each passing moment, he grows stronger still.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:23.23,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,And I know just the princess who can stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.23,0:00:25.66,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I must call in another to stop Tirek.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.66,0:00:28.42,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're talking about me, I presume.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.42,0:00:31.22,Discord,,0,0,0,,Haven't you girls just learned so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.22,0:00:34.59,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And there's something interesting about the sections Discord bookmarked.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:39.11,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Each of you receieved something from the pony whose life you helped change.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.11,0:00:40.76,Twilight,,0,0,0,,There's still one key missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.76,0:00:41.89,Twilight,,0,0,0,,My element.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.89,0:00:43.64,Tirek,,0,0,0,,Join me, Discord,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.83,0:00:46.54,Tirek,,0,0,0,,and reclaim your greatness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.54,0:00:49.15,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Discord has betrayed the ponies of Equestria,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.15,0:00:51.19,Celestia,,0,0,0,,and joined forces with Tirek.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:54.96,Celestia,,0,0,0,,There is no doubt that Tirek is after alicorn magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.96,0:00:57.62,Celestia,,0,0,0,,We must rid ourselves of our magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.62,0:01:00.33,Celestia,,0,0,0,,before Tirek has the chance to steal it from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.07,0:01:43.05,Luna,,0,0,0,,Tirek is set on possessing alicorn magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.05,0:01:46.48,Luna,,0,0,0,,When he comes for us, we cannot have what he is looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.20,0:01:50.34,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm more than willing to do my part and give up my magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.34,0:01:51.72,Luna,,0,0,0,,You misunderstand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.72,0:01:54.64,Luna,,0,0,0,,Our magic cannot just disappear into thin air.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.64,0:01:56.88,Luna,,0,0,0,,Somepony must keep it safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:01:59.51,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,That somepony is you, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.51,0:02:00.64,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.64,0:02:05.98,Celestia,,0,0,0,,We do not believe that Tirek is aware that a fourth alicorn princess exists in Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.98,0:02:10.27,Celestia,,0,0,0,,If we transfer our magic to you, Tirek will not know where it has gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:12.94,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,Do you understand what we're asking of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:15.15,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Yes. It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.15,0:02:18.34,Twilight,,0,0,0,, I'm only now learning how to control my own alicorn magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.34,0:02:19.54,Twilight,,0,0,0,,To take on even more...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.54,0:02:22.80,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,Twilight, you represent the Element of Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.80,0:02:26.23,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,If there is anypony who can do this, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.79,0:02:31.64,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Taking on this task will be one of the most difficult things I will ever do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.64,0:02:33.21,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But with the help of my friends…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.21,0:02:35.05,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Princess Twilight,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.05,0:02:37.93,Celestia,,0,0,0,,but you must keep your new abilities a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.93,0:02:43.07,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I fear that your friends being aware of your new power could put them at great risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.07,0:02:46.68,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Do you still think you can take on this responsibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:49.96,Twilight,,0,0,0,,This is the role I meant to play as a princess of Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:52.25,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I will not fail to do my duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.25,0:02:54.33,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Then we must begin at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:19.80,Discord,,0,0,0,,That can't be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:21.27,Tirek,,0,0,0,,What can't be right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:24.00,Discord,,0,0,0,,Nothing. Carry on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.81,0:03:47.36,Celestia,,0,0,0,,It is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.97,0:03:58.92,Spike,,0,0,0,,You weren't gone very long.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:04:01.26,Spike,,0,0,0,,Does that mean everything is okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:03.51,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Yep. Everything's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.00,0:04:07.82,Spike,,0,0,0,,In that case, I'm going back to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.82,0:04:09.47,Spike,,0,0,0,,Sun's not up...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:11.02,Spike,,0,0,0,,And neither am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.26,0:04:12.51,Twilight,,0,0,0,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.51,0:04:14.43,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The sun should be up by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.16,0:04:16.91,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The sun should be up by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:20.50,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.86,0:04:45.54,Discord,,0,0,0,,Shining Armor, why, whatever are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.54,0:04:47.49,Shining_Armor,,0,0,0,,Back off, traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.49,0:04:51.11,Tirek,,0,0,0,,The only one Discord betrayed was himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.61,0:04:55.65,Tirek,,0,0,0,,Abandoning his true nature to make friends
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.65,0:04:58.98,Tirek,,0,0,0,,with weak-minded equines who offer him nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.21,0:05:13.80,Shining_Armor,,0,0,0,,How could you do this…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.38,0:05:19.04,Tirek,,0,0,0,,Why don't you go and have a little fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:22.09,Tirek,,0,0,0,,I won't stand in your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:39.48,Tirek,,0,0,0,,What have you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:47.82,Tirek,,0,0,0,,Where is your magic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:53.63,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I have to gain better control.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.63,0:05:56.21,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I sure can't practice here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.98,0:05:58.33,Spike,,0,0,0,,Twiligtht?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:05:59.46,Spike,,0,0,0,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:01.27,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh, hi, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.27,0:06:02.64,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Gotta go…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.64,0:06:04.59,Twilight,,0,0,0,,somewhere… else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:12.17,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Twilight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.37,0:06:21.57,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh my goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.57,0:06:22.86,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:24.71,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Jumping junebugs, Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.71,0:06:26.90,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Where did you learn to fly that fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:30.83,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I must have caught a particularly strong breeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.21,0:06:32.46,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.46,0:06:34.26,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Must have been "or something".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.26,0:06:36.75,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Because there wasn't any breeze up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:38.26,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I don't know what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.26,0:06:40.94,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But I don't really have time to figure it out right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.02,0:06:44.50,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Another visit to the Castle of the Two Sisters, I presume?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:47.01,Rarity,,0,0,0,,We'd be more than happy to accompany you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:48.50,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Not today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:50.32,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Tirek may still be a threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.32,0:06:54.36,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I need you all to stay here and encourage everypony to remain inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.30,0:07:06.94,Tirek,,0,0,0,,Getting rid of your magic so that I cannot take it from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:08.53,Tirek,,0,0,0,,That was your plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:11.98,Tirek,,0,0,0,, How does it feel,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.98,0:07:18.08,Tirek,,0,0,0,,knowing that soon every pegasus, unicorn and earth pony will bow to my will?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:21.25,Tirek,,0,0,0,,And that there is nothing you can do to stop it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.59,0:07:23.59,Celestia,,0,0,0,,You will not prevail, Tirek.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.74,0:07:27.13,Tirek,,0,0,0,,Give my regards to Cerberus.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.75,0:07:34.05,Discord,,0,0,0,,You meant "our will".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:35.12,Discord,,0,0,0,,Didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.79,0:07:37.39,Tirek,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.39,0:07:40.11,Tirek,,0,0,0,,Here, I want you to have something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.11,0:07:43.26,Tirek,,0,0,0,,This was given to my by someone very close to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.26,0:07:46.90,Tirek,,0,0,0,,I give it to you as a sign of my gratitude and loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:50.50,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh my. I do love a good accessory.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.50,0:07:53.15,Discord,,0,0,0,,I suppose that's Rarity's influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.06,0:07:56.22,Tirek,,0,0,0,,Amusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.22,0:07:58.43,Tirek,,0,0,0,,But we have no time for such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.43,0:08:01.12,Tirek,,0,0,0,,With the princesses out of the way we can now…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.45,0:08:04.88,Tirek,,0,0,0,,Is this meant to be humorous?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:08.16,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, I haven't touched that one yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.16,0:08:09.38,Tirek,,0,0,0,,There's a fourth?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:11.17,Tirek,,0,0,0,,And you didn't tell me this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.17,0:08:16.24,Discord,,0,0,0,,I just needed some assurance that you truly considered this a team effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:18.38,Discord,,0,0,0,, And now I have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.38,0:08:21.56,Tirek,,0,0,0,,Then where can we find this fourth princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:23.10,Tirek,,0,0,0,,Where's her castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.10,0:08:24.04,Discord,,0,0,0,,Castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.81,0:08:26.14,Discord,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.14,0:08:29.61,Discord,,0,0,0,,Princess Twilight lives above a library in Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.61,0:08:31.14,Discord,,0,0,0,,Castle? Ha-ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:35.90,Tirek,,0,0,0,,Not for much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.68,0:08:43.75,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Alright, y'all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:46.39,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I think we've warned everypony to stay inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.39,0:08:50.67,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Discord will catch Tirek and this will all be over soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:53.82,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I'll bet he takes his sweet time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.82,0:08:56.86,Discord,,0,0,0,,Or perhaps these things just take time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.86,0:08:58.46,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,You're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.46,0:09:00.22,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Did you bring the cucumber sandwiches?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:01.38,Discord,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.90,0:09:06.15,Discord,,0,0,0,,I imagine they'll be your last decent meal for quite some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:11.10,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's that?!\NWhat's going on?\NWhat're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.43,0:09:14.00,Tirek,,0,0,0,,You've gathered up all of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.00,0:09:16.61,Discord,,0,0,0,,And her little dragon too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:19.08,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.08,0:09:21.01,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I thought we were friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.01,0:09:22.32,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh, we were.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.32,0:09:25.72,Discord,,0,0,0,,But Tirek offered me so much more than just tea parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.72,0:09:27.46,Discord,,0,0,0,,Surely you saw this coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:28.72,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.72,0:09:30.63,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I really didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:48.27,Tirek,,0,0,0,,You really think she'd do anything for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.27,0:09:50.91,Discord,,0,0,0,,If Twilight has magic to give,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.91,0:09:52.15,Discord,,0,0,0,,it will be yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:55.57,Discord,,0,0,0,,Soon there won't be a pegasus, earth pony or unicorn
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.57,0:09:59.41,Discord,,0,0,0,,who will be able to stand up against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:00.49,Tirek,,0,0,0,,Us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:03.71,Tirek,,0,0,0,,Who said anything about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.71,0:10:04.59,Discord,,0,0,0,,You did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.39,0:10:07.65,Tirek,,0,0,0,,You helped me grow strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.65,0:10:12.40,Tirek,,0,0,0,,You've provided the means by which I can obtain Princess Twilight's magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:15.34,Tirek,,0,0,0,, And now you are no longer of any use to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:30.02,Discord,,0,0,0,,But you said... this was the sign of your gratitude and loyalty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.17,0:10:33.05,Discord,,0,0,0,,A gift from someone close to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.05,0:10:35.74,Tirek,,0,0,0,,My brother who betrayed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.74,0:10:38.67,Tirek,,0,0,0,,It is as worthless as he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.85,0:10:43.22,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Surely you saw this coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.22,0:10:44.80,Discord,,0,0,0,,I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.80,0:10:46.74,Discord,,0,0,0,,I truly didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.30,0:10:53.65,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:10:59.46,Twilight,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.46,0:11:02.22,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Perfectly controlled teleportation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.78,0:11:10.45,Tirek,,0,0,0,,Princess Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.45,0:11:11.48,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Tirek!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.48,0:11:14.40,Tirek,,0,0,0,,You have something that belongs to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:31.46,Tirek,,0,0,0,,You're going to give me what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.53,0:12:19.09,Tirek,,0,0,0,,Now I understand what your fellow princesses have done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.21,0:13:35.00,Tirek,,0,0,0,,It appears we are at an impasse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:37.92,Tirek,,0,0,0,,How about a trade, Princess Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.34,0:13:44.09,Tirek,,0,0,0,,Their release for all the alicorn magic in Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.26,0:13:49.10,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Don't do that, Twilight! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.10,0:13:52.61,Tirek,,0,0,0,,What's it going to be, Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.64,0:13:58.23,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Don't do it, Twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.23,0:14:00.24,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,We aren't worth it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.24,0:14:02.38,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh but you are, Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.38,0:14:05.69,Discord,,0,0,0,,You are the pony who tought me that friendship is magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.69,0:14:08.24,Discord,,0,0,0,,I had magic and friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:10.58,Discord,,0,0,0,,And now I don't have either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.58,0:14:11.74,Tirek,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.74,0:14:14.75,Tirek,,0,0,0,,I want an answer, and I want it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.60,0:14:29.76,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I will give you my magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:31.93,Twilight,,0,0,0,,In exchange for my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.14,0:14:36.24,Tirek,,0,0,0,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.55,0:14:45.28,Twilight,,0,0,0,,All of my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.49,0:14:50.11,Tirek,,0,0,0,,After the way he has betrayed you, you still call him a friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.47,0:14:51.95,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Release him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.30,0:14:54.54,Tirek,,0,0,0,,If that's what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.38,0:14:57.96,Discord,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.58,0:14:59.93,Discord,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.93,0:15:01.00,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.50,0:15:04.22,Tirek,,0,0,0,,Your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.33,0:15:31.45,Spike,,0,0,0,,Twilight! What were you thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:35.99,Discord,,0,0,0,,Tirek tricked me to believing he could offer me something more valuable than friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:39.84,Discord,,0,0,0,,But there's nothing worth more, I see that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.84,0:15:45.31,Discord,,0,0,0,,He lied when he said this medallion was given as a sign of graditude and loyalty,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.31,0:15:52.22,Discord,,0,0,0,,but when I say that it is a sign of our true friendship, I am telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.25,0:15:58.31,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You think that might be the last one we need?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:16:00.54,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We have to get to the chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.38,0:16:26.00,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Together! I think we have to do this together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:20.72,Tirek,,0,0,0,,How is this possible? You have no magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.72,0:17:22.17,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You're wrong, Tirek.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.17,0:17:24.47,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I may have given you my alicorn magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.47,0:17:27.77,Twilight,,0,0,0,,but I carry within me the most powerful magic of all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.90,0:19:07.08,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Sweet Celestia!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.41,0:19:09.92,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Are you all seeing what I'm seeing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:11.92,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But whose is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.10,0:19:15.54,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I believe, it is yours, Princess Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:21.23,Celestia,,0,0,0,,You've been wondering, what you are meant to do as a princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.23,0:19:22.83,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Do you know now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.83,0:19:28.69,Twilight,,0,0,0,,As princess, I believe, I have the power to spread the magic of friendship across Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.69,0:19:31.19,Twilight,,0,0,0,,That is the role I am meant to have in our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.19,0:19:33.77,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The role I choose to have!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:36.01,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But I didn't defeat Tirek on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.01,0:19:38.33,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It took all of us to unlock the chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.33,0:19:41.82,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Then it is unlikely you are meant to take on this task alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.95,0:19:48.92,Celestia,,0,0,0,,You are now Twilight Sparkle, the Princess of Friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:57.55,Celestia,,0,0,0,,But what is the Princess of Friendship without her friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.51,0:20:09.49,Discord,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, where's my throne?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.49,0:20:11.90,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I don't think you're quite there yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.97,0:20:15.36,Discord,,0,0,0,,Well, I suppose, not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.82,0:20:32.17,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Each one of us has something special\NThat makes us different, that makes us rare
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.17,0:20:39.80,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,We have a light that shines within us\NThat we were always meant to share
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.80,0:20:44.00,Somepony,,0,0,0,,And when we come together\NCombine the light that shines within
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.00,0:20:47.76,Somepony,,0,0,0,,There is nothing we can't do\NThere is no battle we can't win
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:51.40,Somepony,,0,0,0,,And when we come together\NThere'll be a star to guide the way
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.40,0:20:58.04,Somepony,,0,0,0,,It's inside us ev'ry day\NSee it now! See it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.04,0:21:05.54,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Let the rainbow remind you\NThat together we will always shine
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.54,0:21:13.38,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Let the rainbow remind you\NThat forever this will be our time
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.55,0:21:30.35,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Let the rainbow remind you\NThat together we will always shine
